<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>

<record id="theme_iceage.primary_variables_scss" model="theme.ir.asset">
    <field name="key">theme_iceage.primary_variables_scss</field>
    <field name="name">Primary variables SCSS</field>
    <field name="bundle">web._assets_primary_variables</field>
    <field name="path">theme_iceage/static/src/scss/primary_variables.scss</field>
</record>

<record id="theme_iceage.compatibility_saas_11_4_variables_scss" model="theme.ir.asset">
    <field name="key">theme_iceage.compatibility_saas_11_4_variables_scss</field>
    <field name="name">Compatibility saas 11 4 variables SCSS</field>
    <field name="bundle">web._assets_primary_variables</field>
    <field name="path">/theme_iceage/static/src/scss/compatibility-saas-11.4-variables.scss</field>
    <field name="active" eval="False"/>
</record>

<record id="theme_iceage.bootstrap_overridden_scss" model="theme.ir.asset">
    <field name="key">theme_iceage.bootstrap_overridden_scss</field>
    <field name="name">Bootstrap overridden SCSS</field>
    <field name="bundle">web._assets_frontend_helpers</field>
    <field name="directive">prepend</field>
    <field name="path">theme_iceage/static/src/scss/bootstrap_overridden.scss</field>
</record>

</odoo>

<!-- 
    
This XML code is used in Odoo to define assets for a theme named "theme_iceage".
Here's a step-by-step explanation of what the code does:

The <odoo> tag is the root element of the XML file.
All other tags must be enclosed within this tag.

The <record> tags are used to create or update records in a model.
In this case, the model is theme.ir.asset.

Each <record> tag has an id attribute, which is a unique identifier for the record.

The <field> tags within each <record> tag are used to set the values of fields in the record.
The name attribute of the <field> tag is the name of the field,
and the text content of the <field> tag is the value of the field.

In summary, this code is creating or updating three records in the theme.ir.asset model.
These records represent assets for the "theme_iceage" theme.
The assets are SCSS files that are used to style the theme.
The bundle field specifies which asset bundle the asset belongs to,
the path field specifies the location of the SCSS file,
and the active field specifies whether the asset is active.
The directive field in the second record specifies that this asset should be prepended to the bundle.

 -->
